     "group": "Configure shadow password suite parameters",
     "name": "overview",
     "prose": {
      "en": "While a majority of the password control parameters have been moved to PAM, some parameters are still available through the shadow password suite. Any changes made to `/etc/login.defs `will only be applied if the `usermod `command is used. If user IDs are added a different way, use the `chage `command to effect changes to individual user IDs."
